<li id="cite_note-87"><b><a href="#cite_ref-87" title="">^</a></b> Get on your bike! Bicycle- and traffic lessons for foreigners in Tilburg, the Netherlands, Angela van der Kloof, Centre for Foreign Women, Velomondial Conference Proceedings, Amsterdam 2000</li>
<li id="cite_note-88"><b><a href="#cite_ref-88" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.adshel.com/content.aspx?ID=31&amp;ParentID=27&amp;MicrositeID=0&amp;Page=1" class="external text" title="http://www.adshel.com/content.aspx?ID=31&amp;ParentID=27&amp;MicrositeID=0&amp;Page=1" rel="nofollow">Adshel</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Utility_cycling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=28" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFPaul_Niquette1985">Paul Niquette (1985). <i><a href="http://www.niquette.com/certainb/prologue/0text.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.niquette.com/certainb/prologue/0text.htm" rel="nofollow">A Certain Bicyclist: An Offbeat Guide to the Post-Petroleum Age</a></i>. Seven Palms Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0912593040" class="internal">ISBN 0-912593-04-0</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.niquette.com/certainb/prologue/0text.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.niquette.com/certainb/prologue/0text.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.niquette.com/certainb/prologue/0text.htm</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+Certain+Bicyclist%3A+An+Offbeat+Guide+to+the+Post-Petroleum+Age&amp;rft.aulast=Paul+Niquette&amp;rft.au=Paul+Niquette&amp;rft.date=1985&amp;rft.pub=Seven+Palms+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-912593-04-0&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.niquette.com%2Fcertainb%2Fprologue%2F0text.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Utility_cycling"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
